# Task data

- Terminology: **task**, never todo
- **Persistence:** Vercel Blob only (`days/YYYY-MM-DD.json` in Blob). No git-tracked day files.
- **Contract:** `data/schema/day.schema.json`
- **Mutations:** `POST` to task.skarpa.dev API routes (never edit day JSON on disk)
- Task text: actionable line; emphasize keys with `**KEY**`
- Preserve `id` and `jiraKey` when merging; dedupe on `jiraKey`
- Spillover: `source: carryover`, `carriedFrom: <date>`
- Do not close days without explicit user request
- Add manual tasks via `.cursor/skills/add-task/SKILL.md` (`POST /api/task/add`)
- Split one task into focused rows via `.cursor/skills/fragment-task/SKILL.md` (add + remove parent)

## API routes

| Action | Route |
|--------|-------|
| Read day | `GET /api/day` optional `?date=YYYY-MM-DD` |
| Add manual task | `POST /api/task/add` `{ date, text }` |
| Toggle done | `POST /api/task/toggle` `{ date, taskId }` |
| Remove task(s) | `POST /api/task/remove` `{ date, taskId }` or `{ date, taskIds }` |
| Sync Jira topics | `POST /api/task/sync-jira` `{ date, tasks, replaceAll? }` |
| Close day | `POST /api/day/close` `{ date }` |
